      The spelling of the school does not match our records.
    </span>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">
  What you can do next
</h3>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>
    <span class="govuk-body">
      Check the spelling, including any apostrophes or full stops used in the schoolâ€™s name.
